{{Quote|Hey hey! Coming to the celebration? Well either way, Nym wants to make sure everyone has a good time! I've got a bunch of party favors to give out to keep everyone in the spirit.|Nym's Anniversary Quartermaster, to a spacer|<ref name="Star Wars Galaxies">''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]''</ref>}}
[[File:NymsAnniversaryBash-SWG.jpg|thumb|right|250px|The Modal Nodes playing at Nym's Stronghold]]
'''Nym's Anniversary Bash''' was a large anniversary celebration held by [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] warlord [[Nym/Legends|Nym]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lok/Legends|Lok]] in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]].

==History==
[[Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes/Legends|Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes]] played at [[Nym's Base|Nym's Palace]] while the sky above the stronghold was illuminated by a giant [[Fireworks/Legends|fireworks]] display. Nym's quartermaster gave away drinks, [[Cake/Legends|cake]] and small presents to everyone who attended the festivity.

==Behind the scenes==
Nym's Anniversary Bash was an event in the [[Wikipedia:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game|MMORPG]] ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'' to celebrate the 30th anniversary of ''Star Wars''. It took place from [[May 23]] to [[June 30]], [[2007]]. Players that visited Nym's stronghold during that time received a unique badge and could get a small present from Nym's Anniversary Quartermaster once every hour.

